      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Do not stop taking sertraline or start St. John's Wort without first consulting your doctor.** Combining or switching between medications and herbal supplements can cause serious and unpredictable interactions. Both sertraline and St. John's Wort affect serotonin levels, and mixing them can be dangerous. Please discuss your side effects and your interest in alternatives with your prescribing physician before making any changes.",
